text: Antero Immonen (born 15 December 1935) is a Finnish ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Finland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:People from Kotka
